执行流程，很快就能明白的，加油。',0,'1','Duoshuo/1.2:6324232778552443650','',121,1),(124,235,'木头小鬼','','http://t.qq.com/luoyuanhaoustc','124.16.128.66','2016-08-29 21:40:06','2016-08-29 13:40:06','参考<a href=\"https://web.stanford.edu/~jurafsky/slp3/8.pdf\" rel=\"nofollow\">https://web.stanford.edu/~jurafsky/slp3/8.pdf</a> 第13页，应该是aij。但是上面初始化那里下标用的不好，用j会比较好点。',0,'1','Duoshuo/1.2:6324244882751750914','',122,1),(125,181,'武昌鱼股票','dfsfds@126.com','http://jiucaijiucai.com/?武昌鱼股票','223.154.75.83','2016-08-30 06:23:31','2016-08-29 22:23:31',' <img src=\"http://img.t.sinajs.cn/t35/style/images/common/face/ext/normal/24/sweata_org.gif\" />  谢谢，学到了不少东东',0,'1','Duoshuo/1.2:6324379766195487490','',108,0),(126,235,'音之','','http://weibo.com/enchyisle','180.173.3.6','2016-08-30 17:17:51','2016-08-30 09:17:51','sorry， 我没说清楚。不是“算法”部分的“递归计算”。是 Viterbi算法下面第一段，“算法”部分前面的“递归计算”：delta_t+1(i) = max_j [delta_t(j)*a_ij]*b_i(O_t+1)感觉这里的i和j如果是j-&gt;i的话，应该就是a_ji了。',0,'1','Duoshuo/1.2:6324548385063830273','',124,0),(127,235,'木头小鬼','','http://t.qq.com/luoyuanhaoustc','210.77.27.237','2016-08-31 21:43:03','2016-08-31 13:43:03','恩，你说的对，是我敲公式的时候搞错了。谢谢你的指正。',0,'1','Duoshuo/1.2:6324987813318099714','',126,1),(142,224,'卡拉慧子','','http://t.qq.com/kalahuizi','61.181.11.4','2016-09-23 09:52:47','2016-09-23 01:52:47','您好，安装过程第一步就出现问题，求推荐详细的步骤。万分感谢',0,'1','Duoshuo/1.2:6333339739059389186','',0,0),(160,319,'Impala_PostgreSQL_Citus_Postgres-XL 源码分析 | 木头小鬼','','http://www.mutouxiaogui.cn/blog/?p=454','121.42.93.164','2017-01-06 20:25:33','2017-01-06 12:25:33','[&#8230;] Impala 简介 [&#8230;]',0,'1','The Incutio XML-RPC PHP Library -- WordPress/4.5.4','pingback',0,0),(161,417,'Impala_PostgreSQL_Citus_Postgres-XL 源码分析 | 木头小鬼','','http://www.mutouxiaogui.cn/blog/?p=454','121.42.93.164','2017-01-06 20:26:12','2017-01-06 12:26:12','[&#8230;] 查询执行流程 [&#8230;]',0,'1','The Incutio XML-RPC PHP Library -- WordPress/4.5.4','pingback',0,0);
